Chen Mo, why are you so stupid?

287
00:25:47,660 --> 00:25:50,300
Can't you ask her for her phone number?

288
00:25:50,500 --> 00:25:52,940
She told us to ring the bell if anything happens.

289
00:25:53,260 --> 00:25:54,770
It's my thing to ring the bell.

290
00:25:54,770 --> 00:25:56,860
It's your thing to ask her for her phone number.

291
00:25:58,380 --> 00:26:00,700
All right, go to bed after the injection.

292
00:26:01,060 --> 00:26:01,580
Good girl.

293
00:26:02,020 --> 00:26:02,970
Good night.

294
00:26:07,170 --> 00:26:08,420
Dad, it hurts.

295
00:26:08,420 --> 00:26:10,020
Stop pretending. She's gone.

296
00:26:10,020 --> 00:26:10,860
It hurts.

297
00:26:13,620 --> 00:26:14,340
Xi.

298
00:26:14,980 --> 00:26:15,940
-Xi. -It hurts.

299
00:26:16,610 --> 00:26:17,250
Nurse!

300
00:26:17,660 --> 00:26:18,820
It hurts.

301
00:26:19,140 --> 00:26:19,900
Doctor Zhang.

302
00:26:19,900 --> 00:26:20,900
How is my daughter?

303
00:26:21,700 --> 00:26:23,130
She's safe for now.

304
00:26:23,770 --> 00:26:26,140
But your daughter's kidneys keep failing.

305
00:26:26,380 --> 00:26:28,140
Her condition will deteriorate.

306
00:26:28,460 --> 00:26:30,780
If we don't have the transplant in time,

307
00:26:30,780 --> 00:26:32,170
the consequences can be unimaginable.

308
00:26:33,460 --> 00:26:35,820
Have you thought about the thing

309
00:26:36,020 --> 00:26:37,340
I talked to you over the phone last time?

310
00:26:39,900 --> 00:26:40,700
Mr. Chen,

311
00:26:41,260 --> 00:26:43,020
you have to trust my judgment as a doctor.

312
00:26:43,380 --> 00:26:45,900
Your daughter's treatment can't be delayed any longer.

313
00:26:49,810 --> 00:26:50,420
Okay.

314
00:26:52,300 --> 00:26:53,100
Doctor Zhang.

315
00:26:53,900 --> 00:26:54,820
We'll do the surgery right away.

316
00:26:55,690 --> 00:26:56,700
I'll go get the money.

317
00:27:17,080 --> 00:27:19,220
[Zhang Xinyao, Insurance Salesperson, Landlord]

318
00:27:21,020 --> 00:27:22,420
Good for you, Chen Mo.

319
00:27:22,420 --> 00:27:24,100
So you hid all your money here.

320
00:27:24,540 --> 00:27:25,100
Give it to me.

321
00:27:26,140 --> 00:27:26,860
Give it to me.

322
00:27:27,780 --> 00:27:28,460
Give it to me.

323
00:27:29,260 --> 00:27:29,780
You...

324
00:27:30,180 --> 00:27:31,260
Give it to me!

325
00:27:32,580 --> 00:27:33,820
Chen Mo, stop!

326
00:27:39,420 --> 00:27:40,650
Chen Mo, come back!

327
00:27:42,540 --> 00:27:43,780
Chen Mo, come back!

328
00:27:44,740 --> 00:27:45,620
Chen Mo!

329
00:27:49,180 --> 00:27:50,860
There's not enough money. I have to gamble.

330
00:28:08,870 --> 00:28:11,180
[Bank]

331
00:28:18,340 --> 00:28:19,180
Big. Big.

332
00:28:22,250 --> 00:28:23,060
I don't believe it.

333
00:28:23,060 --> 00:28:23,580
Move aside.

334
00:28:23,580 --> 00:28:24,380
Follow me.

335
00:28:24,380 --> 00:28:25,300
Are you crazy?

336
00:28:31,950 --> 00:28:32,640
Come on.

337
00:28:55,060 --> 00:28:55,900
What card is this?

338
00:29:08,340 --> 00:29:09,660
Let it go if you don't have good cards.

339
00:29:14,060 --> 00:29:14,740
All of them.

340
00:29:17,820 --> 00:29:19,410
You don't even dare to look at me.

341
00:29:19,740 --> 00:29:21,180
You must have no good cards.

342
00:29:21,860 --> 00:29:22,500
How about this?

343
00:29:22,860 --> 00:29:23,700
I'll take it.

344
00:29:24,420 --> 00:29:25,140
All of them.

345
00:29:41,860 --> 00:29:42,580
Thank you.

346
00:29:55,580 --> 00:29:57,460
You are a wise man who plays the fool.

347
00:29:57,460 --> 00:29:58,860
I'll get enough money soon.

348
00:29:59,900 --> 00:30:01,420
Good for you.

349
00:30:01,780 --> 00:30:02,580
It feels so good.

350
00:30:09,180 --> 00:30:09,820
Bro,

351
00:30:11,260 --> 00:30:12,540
someone cheated here.

352
00:30:14,450 --> 00:30:15,700
Someone told me you cheated.

353
00:30:21,420 --> 00:30:22,900
Someone cheated here.

354
00:30:22,900 --> 00:30:23,860
No, it's not mine.

355
00:30:25,020 --> 00:30:25,620
What are you doing?

356
00:30:57,730 --> 00:30:58,500
You cheated?

357
00:30:58,500 --> 00:30:59,100
Get lost!

358
00:31:18,780 --> 00:31:19,540
It's him.

359
00:31:26,730 --> 00:31:27,380
Captain Liao.

360
00:31:27,620 --> 00:31:28,500
Here are the materials you asked for.

361
00:31:29,140 --> 00:31:31,260
Chen Mo is a taxi driver.

362
00:31:31,420 --> 00:31:32,810
Her daughter has a kidney disease

363
00:31:32,810 --> 00:31:34,380
and is awaiting a kidney transplant in hospital.

364
00:31:49,780 --> 00:31:50,780
Poor guy.

365
00:31:50,780 --> 00:31:51,620
This engine

366
00:31:51,620 --> 00:31:53,020
is worn out.

367
00:31:53,300 --> 00:31:54,820
I'll deduct 10,000 yuan.

368
00:31:54,980 --> 00:31:56,100
I'm not lying.

369
00:31:56,260 --> 00:31:57,460
It's worn out.

370
00:31:58,580 --> 00:31:59,380
My friend,

371
00:32:00,100 --> 00:32:02,460
your bumper looks so fake.

372
00:32:02,460 --> 00:32:04,460
It falls off when you touch it.

373
00:32:05,660 --> 00:32:07,020
And this window.

374
00:32:07,020 --> 00:32:08,220
It's so cheap.

375
00:32:08,220 --> 00:32:10,010
You can't even raise it up.

376
00:32:10,140 --> 00:32:10,700
Alright.

377
00:32:10,700 --> 00:32:11,780
Just tell me how much you would like to pay.

378
00:32:13,620 --> 00:32:15,460
Since we are friends,

379
00:32:16,300 --> 00:32:17,180
I'll give you

380
00:32:18,380 --> 00:32:19,420
450,000.

381
00:32:19,620 --> 00:32:20,500
So little?

382
00:32:22,220 --> 00:32:23,780
You think it's too little?

383
00:32:23,860 --> 00:32:25,420
I asked you to sell it last year but you didn't sell it.

384
00:32:25,420 --> 00:32:27,220
Last year it could be 650,000.

385
00:32:27,380 --> 00:32:29,460
I offered this price because you're my friend.

386
00:32:30,540 --> 00:32:31,540
Alright, give me the money.

387
00:32:32,740 --> 00:32:34,060
Don't rush.

388
00:32:34,300 --> 00:32:35,850
This is a serious deal.

389
00:32:35,980 --> 00:32:37,620
You need to review the contract first

390
00:32:38,300 --> 00:32:40,020
and sign it.

391
00:32:40,100 --> 00:32:41,420
Then I'll give you the money.

392
00:32:46,820 --> 00:32:47,660
Mr. Yang.

393
00:32:48,380 --> 00:32:49,260
We had an appointment yesterday.

394
00:32:49,260 --> 00:32:49,620
Yes.

395
00:32:49,620 --> 00:32:50,940
Call me when you're done.

396
00:32:50,940 --> 00:32:52,220
No problem.

397
00:32:52,220 --> 00:32:53,180
Remember to write the receipt.

398
00:32:53,980 --> 00:32:54,740
The receipt?

399
00:32:54,740 --> 00:32:55,380
Yes.

400
00:32:55,740 --> 00:32:58,380
You didn't tell me to issue the receipt on the phone yesterday.

401
00:32:58,380 --> 00:33:01,500
Then how should I explain to the insurance company

402
00:33:01,890 --> 00:33:02,380
to raise a claim?

403
00:33:02,380 --> 00:33:04,210
I know you want a claim.

404
00:33:04,210 --> 00:33:05,860
But the price you offered

405
00:33:05,860 --> 00:33:07,260
is not the price for a receipt.

406
00:33:07,260 --> 00:33:08,460
Anyway,

407
00:33:08,460 --> 00:33:09,450
you must give me a receipt.

408
00:33:09,450 --> 00:33:10,620
Mr. Yang.

409
00:33:10,620 --> 00:33:11,970
You know it's not easy

410
00:33:11,970 --> 00:33:12,900
to do a business for us.

411
00:33:12,900 --> 00:33:14,380
If I give you a receipt,

412
00:33:14,380 --> 00:33:15,420
I'll make a loss.

413
00:33:15,420 --> 00:33:16,500
It's not easy for me either.

414
00:33:16,740 --> 00:33:17,500
I don't care.

415
00:33:17,500 --> 00:33:18,060
Come on.

416
00:33:18,060 --> 00:33:18,540
I don't care.

417
00:33:18,540 --> 00:33:19,100
Let me tell you something.

418
00:33:19,100 --> 00:33:20,170
Don't worry, okay?

419
00:33:20,170 --> 00:33:21,580
You're sweating.

420
00:33:21,580 --> 00:33:22,300
I don't care.

421
00:33:22,580 --> 00:33:23,500
Don't worry.

422
00:33:24,580 --> 00:33:25,940
Just add a bit more.

423
00:33:26,220 --> 00:33:28,140
The government wants to develop tourism.

424
00:33:28,140 --> 00:33:29,380
But Mr. Sun,

425
00:33:29,380 --> 00:33:30,420
as an immigrant,

426
00:33:30,420 --> 00:33:32,220
you need to be aware of the situation here first.

427
00:33:34,500 --> 00:33:35,260
Yes.

428
00:33:35,580 --> 00:33:37,540
Mr. Sun, I'm not trying to scare you.

429
00:33:37,540 --> 00:33:38,580
This kind of accident

430
00:33:38,580 --> 00:33:39,860
occurs often

431
00:33:39,860 --> 00:33:41,300
in a drug city like Hua City.

432
00:33:41,300 --> 00:33:42,780
You can have no car or house here,

433
00:33:42,780 --> 00:33:44,460
but you can't live without insurance.

434
00:33:44,460 --> 00:33:44,970
I...

435
00:33:45,500 --> 00:33:46,010
Hello?

436
00:33:46,940 --> 00:33:47,740
Hello?

437
00:34:23,460 --> 00:34:24,780
No wonder I didn't get the deal.

438
00:34:24,780 --> 00:34:25,659
It's you, the jinx,

439
00:34:25,659 --> 00:34:26,659
affecting me.

440
00:34:30,260 --> 00:34:32,300
Miss Zhang, what a coincidence. Are you here to grab some food?

441
00:34:33,860 --> 00:34:34,580
Sit down.

442
00:34:40,300 --> 00:34:40,940
Rent.

443
00:34:45,050 --> 00:34:45,739
I don't have money.

444
00:34:46,100 --> 00:34:47,260
It's been months.

445
00:34:47,620 --> 00:34:48,300
Miss Zhang,

446
00:34:49,250 --> 00:34:50,730
calm down.

447
00:34:51,020 --> 00:34:53,300
I can introduce a business to you.

448
00:34:54,139 --> 00:34:55,060
What business?

449
00:34:56,610 --> 00:34:59,180
I want to buy an insurance.

450
00:35:00,170 --> 00:35:01,500
Can you tell me

451
00:35:01,650 --> 00:35:04,140
how I can get the biggest compensation?

452
00:35:05,420 --> 00:35:06,490
What do you want?

453
00:35:07,420 --> 00:35:08,420
I need money.

454
00:35:09,420 --> 00:35:10,100
Look.

455
00:35:11,300 --> 00:35:13,620
Is my car suitable?

456
00:35:14,460 --> 00:35:15,900
Your poor car

457
00:35:15,900 --> 00:35:17,780
is not worth much even if you drive it to the sea.

458
00:35:17,780 --> 00:35:19,460
You should count in your poor life.

459
00:35:25,060 --> 00:35:26,260
Why didn't I think of that?

460
00:36:52,540 --> 00:36:53,210
Good for you.

461
00:36:53,820 --> 00:36:55,580
You know how to tamper with the brake.

462
00:36:55,860 --> 00:36:57,020
But so far as I know,

463
00:36:58,100 --> 00:36:58,890
you did this

464
00:36:58,890 --> 00:37:00,620
to speed up the damage of tires.

465
00:37:01,540 --> 00:37:03,060
Anyway, it looks like

466
00:37:03,060 --> 00:37:04,540
a deliberate car accident.

467
00:37:06,220 --> 00:37:07,540
Even if I hadn't stopped you

468
00:37:07,540 --> 00:37:08,540
and had let you get the compensation,

469
00:37:09,580 --> 00:37:10,620
after they inspect the situation

470
00:37:10,780 --> 00:37:12,740
and send you the money,

471
00:37:12,900 --> 00:37:14,540
I'm afraid your daughter...

472
00:37:14,540 --> 00:37:15,380
Who are you?

473
00:37:17,620 --> 00:37:18,580
Your name is Chen Mo.

474
00:37:18,980 --> 00:37:19,980
You are a gambler.

475
00:37:20,660 --> 00:37:22,260
You risked your life

476
00:37:22,860 --> 00:37:24,060
for two million?

477
00:37:24,900 --> 00:37:26,410
Who are you?

478
00:37:29,300 --> 00:37:30,610
If I tell you

479
00:37:31,260 --> 00:37:32,980
I can save your daughter,

480
00:37:33,540 --> 00:37:35,100
would you like to bet with me?

481
00:37:43,820 --> 00:37:45,220
You don't look like someone

482
00:37:45,220 --> 00:37:46,900
who can give me two million at once.

483
00:38:12,780 --> 00:38:13,300
Fine.

484
00:38:14,180 --> 00:38:14,820
I bet.

485
00:38:15,300 --> 00:38:16,500
Don't be happy too soon.

486
00:38:17,220 --> 00:38:18,580
You can only get the money when you win.

487
00:38:19,660 --> 00:38:20,300
What do you want to bet on?

488
00:38:22,340 --> 00:38:23,900
I bet you are another person.

489
00:38:24,100 --> 00:38:24,940
You're not Chen Mo.

490
00:38:30,140 --> 00:38:31,020
Then who am I?

491
00:38:32,340 --> 00:38:33,010
Luo Xiang.

492
00:38:39,540 --> 00:38:40,570
Don't overthink.

493
00:38:40,860 --> 00:38:42,100
It's not that complicated.

494
00:38:42,620 --> 00:38:44,380
You're just Liang Long's follower.

495
00:38:44,380 --> 00:38:45,980
It's called the Dark Night Project.

496
00:38:46,420 --> 00:38:48,900
It's my personal act to make you my informant.

497
00:38:52,700 --> 00:38:53,260
I'm sorry.

498
00:38:53,260 --> 00:38:55,020
I can't help you with this.

499
00:38:57,060 --> 00:38:58,060
Are you afraid of death?

500
00:38:59,300 --> 00:39:01,180
Didn't you die once a minute ago?

501
00:39:06,260 --> 00:39:08,220
I know about your daughter.

502
00:39:09,060 --> 00:39:12,180
Don't you want to see her grow up happily?

503
00:39:13,740 --> 00:39:15,700
If you hesitate for one more minute,

504
00:39:15,940 --> 00:39:16,740
you'll miss

505
00:39:16,740 --> 00:39:18,940
a minute for her to live.

506
00:39:19,940 --> 00:39:20,780
Do you think

507
00:39:20,780 --> 00:39:23,010
she can wait until the next kidney transplant?

508
00:39:27,210 --> 00:39:29,340
But those drug criminals are so scary.

509
00:39:29,730 --> 00:39:31,060
If they know my daughter,

510
00:39:31,260 --> 00:39:32,420
she will lose her life.

511
00:39:32,420 --> 00:39:33,980
Don't worry about that.

512
00:39:34,460 --> 00:39:36,250
We will have a seamless plan

513
00:39:36,250 --> 00:39:37,620
to protect our informants

514
00:39:37,620 --> 00:39:39,180
and their family members.

515
00:39:39,810 --> 00:39:41,020
How can you guarantee

516
00:39:41,020 --> 00:39:42,100
that you can protect them?

517
00:39:42,740 --> 00:39:44,300
There are so many drug criminals in Hua City.

518
00:39:44,300 --> 00:39:45,420
You can't catch them all.

519
00:39:46,100 --> 00:39:46,740
I'm sorry.

520
00:39:47,660 --> 00:39:49,020
Don't make it difficult for me.

521
00:39:53,460 --> 00:39:55,020
Am I against the law not being an informant?

522
00:39:55,860 --> 00:39:57,140
You broke the insurance law,

523
00:39:57,140 --> 00:39:58,220
fabricated the scene,

524
00:39:58,860 --> 00:40:00,180
and destroyed public property.

525
00:40:01,510 --> 00:40:05,330
[Police Department]

526
00:40:02,140 --> 00:40:04,460
Our policemen had to return

527
00:40:04,700 --> 00:40:06,060
shortly after they went out on patrol.

528
00:40:05,790 --> 00:40:07,510
[Deputy Director Sha's Office]

529
00:40:06,290 --> 00:40:08,060
Because they can't even afford gas.

530
00:40:08,780 --> 00:40:09,260
Really?

531
00:40:09,900 --> 00:40:10,540
Come in.

532
00:40:11,330 --> 00:40:12,060
Someone is here.

533
00:40:12,060 --> 00:40:12,860
I have to hang up.

534
00:40:14,860 --> 00:40:15,660
Officer Yu.

535
00:40:17,760 --> 00:40:19,400
[Yu Shenghai, Member of the Action Squad]

536
00:40:18,820 --> 00:40:19,730
Hi, Deputy Director Sha.

537
00:40:20,420 --> 00:40:21,410
Welcome to my place.

538
00:40:21,940 --> 00:40:22,860
You know what?

539
00:40:22,940 --> 00:40:24,540
I put aside all the business today

540
00:40:24,540 --> 00:40:25,980
just to wait for you.

541
00:40:26,450 --> 00:40:27,540
Come, have a seat.

542
00:40:31,660 --> 00:40:32,500
Wait a minute.

543
00:40:35,940 --> 00:40:37,340
Be gentle.

544
00:40:37,340 --> 00:40:38,340
Don't break it.

545
00:40:38,740 --> 00:40:39,490
Okay.

546
00:40:39,390 --> 00:40:41,780
[Deputy Director Sha, Deputy Director of the Hua City Police Department]

547
00:40:39,740 --> 00:40:41,500
I'm telling you. It is expensive.

548
00:40:42,850 --> 00:40:44,100
Look at them.

549
00:40:45,340 --> 00:40:46,060
Officer Yu,

550
00:40:46,460 --> 00:40:48,700
do you know why I transferred you back?

551
00:40:50,340 --> 00:40:52,060
The government plans to

552
00:40:52,060 --> 00:40:53,820
turn Hua City into a tourist city

553
00:40:53,820 --> 00:40:54,900
to speed up economic growth.

554
00:40:55,380 --> 00:40:57,180
What is the most important for a tourist city?

555
00:40:57,740 --> 00:40:59,620
Safety, service and stability.

556
00:41:00,260 --> 00:41:00,900
However,

557
00:41:00,900 --> 00:41:03,420
Hua City is still affected by the Golden Triangle.

558
00:41:03,780 --> 00:41:05,660
It's hard to create a good social environment

559
00:41:05,980 --> 00:41:09,380
and change the public's impression of Hua City.

560
00:41:10,900 --> 00:41:12,020
So at this time,

561
00:41:13,020 --> 00:41:14,540
someone suggested to me

562
00:41:15,940 --> 00:41:18,500
that Hua City needs a symbol.

563
00:41:19,140 --> 00:41:19,700
Here you go.

564
00:41:20,380 --> 00:41:21,220
Have some coffee.

565
00:41:22,180 --> 00:41:24,900
And you are this symbol.

566
00:41:27,260 --> 00:41:28,010
Let me tell you.

567
00:41:28,340 --> 00:41:29,020
Look.

568
00:41:29,020 --> 00:41:31,140
You are the ambassador of the police force

569
00:41:31,660 --> 00:41:32,820
and also a pioneer of the anti-drug police.

570
00:41:33,500 --> 00:41:34,980
I believe your presence

571
00:41:35,220 --> 00:41:36,780
will be a threat

572
00:41:36,900 --> 00:41:38,500
to those criminals,

573
00:41:38,500 --> 00:41:40,460
especially to those drug criminals.

574
00:41:40,700 --> 00:41:43,020
At the same time,

575
00:41:43,020 --> 00:41:44,940
you'll be a role model to your colleagues.

576
00:41:45,250 --> 00:41:46,820
So I applied to my superiors

577
00:41:46,820 --> 00:41:48,140
to transfer you back.

578
00:41:49,300 --> 00:41:50,740
I won't let you down.

579
00:41:50,820 --> 00:41:51,940
Here, have some coffee.

580
00:41:55,260 --> 00:41:56,100
Do you know

581
00:41:56,700 --> 00:41:58,260
who suggested this to me?

582
00:41:59,620 --> 00:42:00,370
Well,

583
00:42:00,460 --> 00:42:02,220
you two were close.

584
00:42:02,260 --> 00:42:03,060
Five years ago,

585
00:42:03,060 --> 00:42:05,140
you two solved a case together.

586
00:42:05,580 --> 00:42:07,180
The Kuntuo case.

587
00:42:11,380 --> 00:42:12,420
Officer Liao.

588
00:42:13,940 --> 00:42:14,820
Liao Yongjia?

589
00:42:14,900 --> 00:42:15,580
Yes.

590
00:42:15,780 --> 00:42:18,340
And he's your superior this time.

591
00:42:19,180 --> 00:42:19,980
Deputy Director Sha,

592
00:42:20,180 --> 00:42:21,380
I want to apply for a transfer.

593
00:42:21,380 --> 00:42:22,740
I can't work under him.

594
00:42:23,100 --> 00:42:23,900
Why?

595
00:42:25,100 --> 00:42:26,380
He's a nut.

596
00:42:27,780 --> 00:42:28,620
Officer Yu,

597
00:42:28,820 --> 00:42:30,620
you're exaggerating.

598
00:42:30,780 --> 00:42:32,140
Officer Liao

599
00:42:32,140 --> 00:42:33,700
is a bit aggressive

600
00:42:33,900 --> 00:42:35,420
and has a weird temper.

601
00:42:36,220 --> 00:42:37,500
But think about it.

602
00:42:37,620 --> 00:42:38,500
In Hua City,

603
00:42:38,700 --> 00:42:40,140
if you don't work hard,

604
00:42:40,140 --> 00:42:41,420
how can you make achievements,

605
00:42:41,420 --> 00:42:42,100
right?

606
00:42:42,860 --> 00:42:44,180
So, trust me.

607
00:42:44,420 --> 00:42:45,100
If you follow him,

608
00:42:46,100 --> 00:42:48,060
you'll even impress the city more.

609
00:43:07,140 --> 00:43:10,750
[Yu Shenghai; Poster Against Gambling, Prostitution and Drugs]

610
00:43:43,980 --> 00:43:44,660
Captain Liao.

611
00:43:44,940 --> 00:43:45,780
A file for you.

612
00:43:50,100 --> 00:43:51,620
Has the time of Tian's death been confirmed?

613
00:43:51,980 --> 00:43:53,180
The forensic said

614
00:43:53,180 --> 00:43:54,940
it was two days before the explosion.

615
00:43:55,340 --> 00:43:56,770
The first scene of crime wasn't the bar.

616
00:43:57,740 --> 00:43:58,500
Captain Liao.

617
00:43:58,500 --> 00:43:59,460
We found something new.

618
00:44:11,420 --> 00:44:12,180
Officer Liao.

619
00:44:12,180 --> 00:44:13,260
I'm Yu Shenghai.

620
00:44:14,860 --> 00:44:17,300
Find out all the blind spots of the camera.

621
00:44:17,570 --> 00:44:18,610
They're the focus of the investigation.

622
00:44:21,100 --> 00:44:21,740
Sorry.

623
00:44:22,140 --> 00:44:23,420
I should have come here yesterday.

624
00:44:24,380 --> 00:44:25,330
Stop investigating.

625
00:44:25,740 --> 00:44:26,780
Go to the forensic department

626
00:44:26,980 --> 00:44:28,300
and get the bomb report.

627
00:44:28,300 --> 00:44:28,900
Yes.

628
00:44:35,900 --> 00:44:36,660
What's wrong?

629
00:44:38,180 --> 00:44:39,580
Someone took revenge on me yesterday.

630
00:44:39,580 --> 00:44:40,250
I got shot.

631
00:44:40,980 --> 00:44:42,500
I'm afraid I can't work,

632
00:44:42,500 --> 00:44:44,300
so I'm here to resign today.

633
00:44:44,700 --> 00:44:45,290
Captain Liao.

634
00:44:46,460 --> 00:44:48,260
The man you brought back yesterday wants to see you.

635
00:44:48,700 --> 00:44:49,420
Which one?

636
00:44:49,420 --> 00:44:50,330
The one who tried to defraud an insurance company.
